{"tid":1575862,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日午餐，大廚小妹親自下廚煎牛扒","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T17:11:37.000Z","uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb93feff930a66a48f14f4c7be16b2e50ab2c500","tid":1575862,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"差唔多有成隻手掌咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對於小妹呢個牛魔王黎講實在是極度誘惑<br />\n五成熟火候控制得宜<br />\n肥瘦比例剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n色澤粉嫩<br />\n肉質鬆軟<br />\n肉汁豐盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛味香濃<br />\n簡單加幾粒岩鹽同胡椒已經好美味<br />\n啖啖都是極致滋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是小妹近年品嚐過<br />\n近乎煎得最好的一塊牛扒<br />\n係唔知點解煎嗰時自動分開一半<br />\n而伴碟既蕃茄都唔馬虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n濃濃的香味<br />\n幼滑中帶清甜<br />\n會添上唔同味道有中和濃膩之效<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DwMhv4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwMhv4Q.jpg&h=9ff1e0d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a3760ed894623f50c394bbb085a54e4c4c1518c","tid":1575862,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f2c13cce0c7d0d2ea0ade1acb4eec8f0ec04da3","tid":1575862,"uid":21886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又食"},{"pid":"22d7ed1eccbba1f3f295128e07ea16fedb327563","t